{"TopicId":204776,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Am I the only one who is annoyed by the \u0026quot;new\u0026quot; forums update?","CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-10T15:39:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-10T15:39:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did the \u0022Levels\u0022 of users go? (I forgot how they\u0027re called). Where did scrollable signatures go? Why does the forums seem buggy with this update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt just doesn\u0027t seem right. I know that for most of you this may be a minor issue, but for me... Oh boy. That hurts. With this design update some of the fun of the forums has gone away. I was just used to the older version. I don\u0027t know how about you guys, is this liquiding you off too? Why did they even have to do that, it was okay. Kinda like mobile version of YouTube, if you know what I mean.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-10T17:34:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the biathlon targets above the photo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-10T21:47:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\njust checking to see if my beneath the planet of the apes reference is still intact.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmeh, close enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif only there was a dark theme so im not so distracted by my eye floaties.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-10T21:49:19Z\u0022 title=\u002209/10/2021 09:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 10, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-11T07:01:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis update broke so much, why did they even have to do that when everyone wwas already satisfied with their experience?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-11T13:24:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nForum updates are critical for security reasons, and almost universally come with \u0022features\u0022 that break custom forum setups and change vanilla ones.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s just a fact of the internet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-11T13:24:58Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2021 01:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Superfluous J\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-11T20:31:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224030569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631366681\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nForum updates are critical for security reasons, and almost universally come with \u0022features\u0022 that break custom forum setups and change vanilla ones.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s just a fact of the internet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni just wish when they used this excuse they would only update security.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-11T20:32:04Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2021 08:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-12T10:59:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224030679\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631392293\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni just wish when they used this excuse they would only update security.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I was so used to the older layout and now alot of functions and things are missing or broken, it\u0027s basically unacceptable\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-12T18:19:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224030679\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631392293\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni just wish when they used this excuse they would only update security.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t \u0022only update security.\u0022 You update and get everything or don\u0027t update and get hacked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-12T19:23:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224030988\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631470775\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t \u0022only update security.\u0022 You update and get everything or don\u0027t update and get hacked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlinux has been doing it for years. you can upgrade the security at the kernel level and leave everything else alone.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-12T19:24:49Z\u0022 title=\u002209/12/2021 07:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 12, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-13T23:01:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224031009\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631474613\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/12/2021 at 3:23 PM, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlinux has been doing it for years. you can upgrade the security at the kernel level and leave everything else alone.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry I should have been more clear.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t \u0022update security\u0022 with forum software. You can with Linux because Linux is written to do that. Forum software is not and I doubt it ever will be.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-14T05:21:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill can\u0027t see any connection between the (access rights and buffer overflows) and GUI.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-14T08:11:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224031622\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631596864\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill can\u0027t see any connection between the (access rights and buffer overflows) and GUI.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe connection is that they\u0027re both in the single update that is available and you choose to get both or neither.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}